mapper.update: UPDATE "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" AS DbT3070 SET DbT3070."jikoFutanSeiriNo" = "", DbT3070."jikoFutanSeiriNo" = "" WHERE DbT3070."dataSakuseiKubun" = '1' AND DbT3070."shomeisho_UketoriYM" = #{処理年月} AND DbT3070."jikoFutanSeiriNo" is not null

select.id: select高額合算自己負担額一時と明細データ

mapper.select:
SELECT ,
FROM DbWT37H1KogakuGassanaJikofutangaku AS DbWT37H1 LEFT JOIN(( SELECT rowNum.* FROM( SELECT DbT3070.*, row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY DbT3070."hihokenshaNo"DbT3070."taishoNendo"DbT3070."hokenshaNo"DbT3070."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" ORDER BY DbT3070."rirekiNo" DESC) AS rrkno FROM rgdb."DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" AS DbT3070 ) AS rowNum WHERE T."dataSakuseiKubun" = '1' AND T."shomeisho_UketoriYM" is null, AND T."hoseiZumi_SofuYM" is not null )AS GETSAI) ON DbWT37H1.hokenshaNoIn = GETSAI."hihokenshaNo" AND DbWT37H1.taishoNendo = GETSAI."taishoNendo" AND DbWT37H1.shoKisaiHokenshaNo = GETSAI."hokenshaNo" AND DbWT37H1.shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo = GETSAI."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" WHERE GETSAI.rowNum = 1

SELECT , FROM (SELECT DbWT137H2.* DbWT137H1.rirekiNo FROM rgdb."DbWT37H2KogakuGassanaJikofutangakuMeisai" AS DbWT137H2 INNER JOIN rgdb."DbWT37H1KogakuGassanaJikofutangaku" AS DbWT137H1 ON DbWT137H2."renban" = DBWT137H1."renban" WHERE DBWT137H1."koshinFlag" = true) AS MEISAI INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" AS DbT3070 ON MEISAI."hokenshaNoIn" = DbT3070."hihokenshaNo" AND MEISAI."taishoNendo" = DbT3070."taishoNendo" AND MEISAI."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = DbT3070."hokenshaNo" AND MEISAI."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" = DbT3070."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" AND MEISAI."rirekiNo" = DbT3070."rirekiNo" AND MEISAI."taishoM" = DbT3070."taishoM" WHERE MEISAI."jikoFutanGaku" <> (DbT3070."sumi_Gokei_JikoFutanGaku" - DbT3070."sumi_Gokei_Under70KogakuShikyuGaku") GROUP BY MEISAI."renban"

SELECT
FROM "DbWT37H1KogakuGassanaJikofutangaku" AS DbWT37H1 INNER JOIN "DbWT0001Hihokensha" AS DbWT0001 ON DbWT37H1."renban" = DbWT0001."meisaiRenban" ${出力順}
